trans-unit.source: Specifies where a chart element, such as a legend or title, will be docked on the chart.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvor et diagramelement, for eksempel en forklaring eller tittel, forankret i diagrammet.

trans-unit.source: The Docking enumeration represents the location on the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control where a chart element will be docked.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen forankring representerer plasseringen på den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontrollen der et diagramelement er forankret.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: Set the `IsDockedInsideChartArea` property of the relevant chart element to specify whether that element will be docked to the entire chart image or to a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea>object.
trans-unit.target: Angi den `IsDockedInsideChartArea` -egenskapen til det aktuelle diagramelementet til å angi om dette elementet forankret til hele diagrambildet eller til en <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea>

trans-unit.source: The chart area is specified in the `DockedToChartArea` property of the chart element.
trans-unit.target: Diagramområdet er angitt i den `DockedToChartArea` for diagramelementet.

trans-unit.source: Docked to the bottom of either the chart image or a <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Forankret til bunnen av enten diagrambildet eller <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Docked to the left of either the chart image or a <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Forankret til venstre for enten diagrambildet eller <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Docked to the right of either the chart image or a <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Forankret til høyre for enten diagrambildet eller <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Docked to the top of either the chart image or a <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Forankret til toppen av enten diagrambildet eller <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"> </xref> objektet.
